import os

path = "/Users/lizard0827"

i = 0
for (root, dirs, files) in os.walk(path):
    for names in dirs:
        print(os.path.join(root, names))
    print (root)
    print (files)
    print ("----")
    i += 1
    if i >= 4:
        break

df = df.sort_values(by= 'Gold', ascending = False)
df.head()
df.index[0]

df = df[(df['Gold']>0)& (df['Gold.1']>0)]
df['difference1'] = (df['Gold']-df['Gold.1']).abs()
df.sort_values (by ='difference1', ascending = False)
df.head()
df['difference1'].idxmax()

census_df = pd.read_csv('census.csv')
census_df.head()
census_df = census_df[census_df['SUMLEV']==50]
census_df.head()
x = census_df.groupby('STNAME').count()['CTYNAME']
ans = x.idxmax()
ans

top_census_df= census_df.sort_values(by=['STNAME', 'CENSUS2010POP'], ascending = False)
top_census_df = top_census_df.groupby('STNAME').head(3)
ans = top_census_df.groupby('STNAME').sum().sort_values(by ='CENSUS2010POP', ascending = False).head(3).index.tolist()
ans

census_df = pd.read_csv('census.csv')
census_df.head()
census_df = census_df[census_df['SUMLEV']==50]
census_df['max']= census_df[['POPESTIMATE2010', 'POPESTIMATE2011', 'POPESTIMATE2012', 'POPESTIMATE2013', 'POPESTIMATE2014', 'POPESTIMATE2015']].max(axis=1)
census_df['min']= census_df[['POPESTIMATE2010', 'POPESTIMATE2011', 'POPESTIMATE2012', 'POPESTIMATE2013', 'POPESTIMATE2014', 'POPESTIMATE2015']].min(axis=1)
census_df['difference']=census_df['max']-census_df['min']
census_df = census_df.sort_values(by ='difference', ascending = False)
census_df.iloc[0]['CTYNAME']
